values.text:
Dear friend,
I'm glad the portal worked.
If you're reading this then 
things haven't turned out 
as we hoped. This world
is different from the one 
you remember. We don't
have much time, start in 
3...2...1...0  Go! Go! Go!

Everything changed
when our planet 
became a threat to
others, their thirst
for power drained
our civilisation dry. 
When the timer turns
red you can see 
inside the alien chest.
Be careful!

We don't have much
time. The human
race is at stake. 
You must find my 
secret laboratory 
and turn on the 
time machine!
2019 is the key
you need...
Good luck!

It's 2034, fifteen 
years since the first 
invasion. The rest of 
us have been hiding
underground but this 
year will be our last. 
Extinction is imminent. 
You must find a way 
back, remember this 
fateful year, 2034.

Great! 
You're close
to the secret 
laboratory...
Watch out for
the aliens
they mustn't 
find my machine...

finding your
way is as 
easy as pi
III I IV II

My dear friend
Everything is in
your hands now. 
Will you save us?
Travel back in time
so that humankind
can have a future. 

X = 100 x 20 + 19 + 1^3

Pay attention to the
numbers in my
notes, they are the
key to opening the
doors!

Pi will take you
to the sky

Congratulations! You did it!
You sent the time machine 
to the year 2019 where I'll 
be waiting for it. Thanks to 
you and the car the human 
race can now be saved!

find the remote 
control to activate
the time machine!

Back To The Past

     created by
KJWalker & FGR3D

For next challenge
"/goto next"
in chat window
